{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_12_02",
  "title": "小美山愛 2話 タンク岡本さん！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――さらに数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――さらに数日後",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（今日は愛の練習に付き合う日だが……）\n（ん？　なぜレッスンスタジオに分厚いマットが？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（今日は愛の練習に付き合う日だが……）\n（ん？　なぜレッスンスタジオに分厚いマットが？）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.5666667183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4リズノワの筋肉が、今宵はリングで輝く！\n戦うアイドル～！　小美山～～愛～～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "BIG4リズノワの筋肉が、今宵はリングで輝く！\n戦うアイドル～！　小美山～～愛～～！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.233333385,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5066.6666746,
          "startTime": 15.1666667183
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2833.3333332999987,
          "startTime": 18.0666667183
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、愛が出てきた……これは、レスラーの選手入場か\n入場曲で雰囲気を盛り上げて、実況までしてるんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あ、愛が出てきた……これは、レスラーの選手入場か\n入場曲で雰囲気を盛り上げて、実況までしてるんだな",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.6666667183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ{user}さん、行きますね！\n準備はいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "それじゃあ{user}さん、行きますね！\n準備はいいですか？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.933333385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "準備？　どういうことだ……？\nまさか飛ぶのか！？　そ、その技は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "準備？　どういうことだ……？\nまさか飛ぶのか！？　そ、その技は……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2666667183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "ムーンサルトプレスですっ！\n受けて下さい！ 　{user}さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ムーンサルトプレスですっ！\n受けて下さい！ 　{user}さん！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "がはっ！　潰れる、潰れる～！\nギブアップ、ギブアップだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "がはっ！　潰れる、潰れる～！\nギブアップ、ギブアップだ！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.0666667183,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 49.8000000437
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "見事に決まったーーー！　愛選手の必殺技っ！\n豪快に相手選手がマットに沈んでいくぅーーー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "見事に決まったーーー！　愛選手の必殺技っ！\n豪快に相手選手がマットに沈んでいくぅーーー！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.4666667183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか、この分厚いマットはこのために……\n実戦って、技の練習のことか……死ぬかと思ったよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そ、そうか、この分厚いマットはこのために……\n実戦って、技の練習のことか……死ぬかと思ったよ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.233333385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "どうですか、{user}さん！\n私のプロレス技は！　綺麗に決まりましたよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "どうですか、{user}さん！\n私のプロレス技は！　綺麗に決まりましたよね！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.5333303333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "最後の技、俺の首を太腿で挟んで大回転していたが\nあれは……『フランケンシュタイナー』か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "最後の技、俺の首を太腿で挟んで大回転していたが\nあれは……『フランケンシュタイナー』か？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "それにアレンジを加えた私のオリジナル技ですよ！\n名付けて『マッスル・愛・シュタイナー』ですっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "それにアレンジを加えた私のオリジナル技ですよ！\n名付けて『マッスル・愛・シュタイナー』ですっ！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.0666636666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに気合い入り過ぎじゃないか！？\n聞いたことないぞ、技を開発するアイドルなんて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "さすがに気合い入り過ぎじゃないか！？\n聞いたことないぞ、技を開発するアイドルなんて！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9333303333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "でも必殺技の一つくらいあった方が\nファンも会場も盛り上がると思うんですよっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "でも必殺技の一つくらいあった方が\nファンも会場も盛り上がると思うんですよっ！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.5666636666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "た、確かに、話題にはなりそうだ\n愛の熱意とやる気がファンに伝わるしな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "た、確かに、話題にはなりそうだ\n愛の熱意とやる気がファンに伝わるしな……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3333303333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよねっ！　よし、じゃあ続きをしましょう！\n行きますよ～{user}さ～ん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そうですよねっ！　よし、じゃあ続きをしましょう！\n行きますよ～{user}さ～ん！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.499997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "お、おい、まだやるのか！？\nちょ、ちょっと休憩を……ぐおおっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "お、おい、まだやるのか！？\nちょ、ちょっと休憩を……ぐおおっ！？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.2666616321,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 127.8333221873
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4500.0061115000135,
