      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.8333303333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.9333303333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "仕上がりは……かんっぺきです！\n見て下さい、エルボーのキレを！　シュッシュッ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "仕上がりは……かんっぺきです！\n見て下さい、エルボーのキレを！　シュッシュッ！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.4333303333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.4333303333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "滑らか過ぎるシャドーにくっきりした筋肉……\n素人目でもハッキリ分かる仕上がり方だ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "滑らか過ぎるシャドーにくっきりした筋肉……\n素人目でもハッキリ分かる仕上がり方だ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.899997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.2666422964
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "セコンド、最後に気合いを注入して下さい！\n私の初出場と初勝利を祈って……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "セコンド、最後に気合いを注入して下さい！\n私の初出場と初勝利を祈って……！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.999997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "はは、気持ちはもう完璧にプロレスラーだな\nよし、頑張って来い！　ラウンドガール！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "はは、気持ちはもう完璧にプロレスラーだな\nよし、頑張って来い！　ラウンドガール！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.899997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.4333089631
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "え？　らうんど……？　らうんどがーる？\nわ、私ってプロレスラーとして戦うはずじゃ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "え？　らうんど……？　らうんどがーる？\nわ、私ってプロレスラーとして戦うはずじゃ……？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.1333303333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174.7666422964
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんな訳ないだろう！？　所属アイドルを\n戦わせるなんて……え？　もしかして愛……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そ、そんな訳ないだろう！？　所属アイドルを\n戦わせるなんて……え？　もしかして愛……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.499997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
